headline: Intuit stock rises following GoCo acquisition deal
summary: Investing.com -- Shares of Intuit Inc (NASDAQ:INTU) climbed 3.3% as the company announced its agreement to acquire GoCo, a provider of HR and benefits solutions aimed at bolstering its Human Capital Management offerings. The move is seen as a strategic effort to expand Intuit’s services to mid-market businesses through its Intuit Enterprise Suite and QuickBooks Payroll.

headline: Intuit shares move higher as HSBC upgrades stock to Buy on attractive valuation
summary: Investing.com -- HSBC has raised its rating on Intuit (NASDAQ:INTU) to Buy from Hold, a move driven by the company’s compelling valuation and limited exposure to tariff woes.
